This is a function meant to respond to the user's input
The scanario is that one or more iplot windows are open that show (related) projections obtained from cepp
The user's interaction options (widget) are the following
He ask the widget to open a new iplot device
He can click on an iplot device and set to be the current one for plotting
He can choose choose fixed sets of arbitrary size by selecting in any of the graphs (isets)
The number should be settable in the backend via closures
The process starts with user calling the function 'slider' with a specified num

